[h3]Naming Variables[/h3] You can use these variables in the naming pattern: [list] [*][b]{transportType}[/b]: Mode of transport (RP, RC, TP, TC, WP, WC, AP, AC, UNK, etc.) [*][b]{cargoTypes}[/b]: Cargo being carried (separated by configurable character) [*][b]{townNames}[/b]: Connected town names [*][b]{lineType}[/b]: Line classification [*][b]{lineNumber}[/b]: Unique line ID [/list]

