[h2]Troubleshooting[/h2] [list] [*][b]No rename[/b]: Check for custom name or [b][NoAuto][/b] prefix [*][b]Wrong cargo[/b]: Wait for vehicle loading or use manual rename [*][b]Town name issues[/b]: Verify stop connections [/list]

[h2]FAQ[/h2] [b]Q[/b]: How do I disable auto-naming for specific lines? [list] [*][b]A[/b]: Add [b][NoAuto][/b] prefix to line name. You can change this in settings. [/list]

[b]Q[/b]: Why are cargo types not detected correctly? [list] [*][b]A[/b]: Wait for vehicles to load cargo or use manual rename. Cargo types are detected after vehicles load cargo. [/list]

[b]Q[/b]: How can I rename lines manually? [list] [*][b]A[/b]: Set line name to [b]r[/b] or [b]reload[/b] and click - unclick the add stop button. [*][b]A[/b]: Use default names ([b]Line 1[/b], [b]UNK[/b]). [/list]

